@andimarek @felipe-gdr  - thoughts on this code pattern??
My aim is to not lock - so possible that IF a DataFetchingEnv some how crossed threads then its possible that 2 reads cause 2 supplier reads.  But its lock free and I think MOST cases will be read on the thread that has the DF
To be pathological, you would need to read it on thread A and then read it again on thread B.

